            <div type="transcript" id="F215A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I shall know why - when Time<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is over -</l>
                    <l>And I have ceased to wonder<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 why - </l>
                    <l>Christ will explain each separate<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 anguish </l>
                    <l>In the fair schoolroom of the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 sky - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He will tell me what &quot;Peter&quot; promised -</l>
                    <l>And I - for wonder at his woe - </l>
                    <l>I shall forget the drop<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of anguish </l>
                    <l>That scalds me now - that<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 scalds me now!  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
